title: IAA Tonight | LeBron, AD and Russell Westbrook 'Huddle Up' and Commit to Winning in LA
description: It was revealed that LeBron James, Anthony Davis, and Russell Westbrook "huddled up" on a phone call recently and expressed their commitment to one another, but will that call make them any better than last season? Auntie Chantel Tremitiere, Leger Douzable, and LeSean McCoy discuss what needs to happen for them in order to win. Plus, we have some burning questions for the 2022 NFL season, and Shady doesn't hold back on former NFL running back Ricky Williams for his recent comments.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Auntie Chantel Tremitiere, Leger Douzable, LeSean McCoy)
